Package org.tensorflow.demo

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CameraConnectionFragment.ConnectionCallback
    Callback for Activities to use to initialize their data once the selected preview size is known.
    Classifier
    Generic interface for interacting with different recognition engines.
    OverlayView.DrawCallback
    Interface defining the callback for client classes.
    ResultsView  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoFitTextureView
    A TextureView that can be adjusted to a specified aspect ratio.
    CameraActivity  
    CameraConnectionFragment  
    CameraConnectionFragment.ErrorDialog
    Shows an error message dialog.
    Classifier.Recognition
    An immutable result returned by a Classifier describing what was recognized.
    ClassifierActivity  
    DetectorActivity
    An activity that uses a TensorFlowMultiBoxDetector and ObjectTracker to detect and then track objects.
    LegacyCameraConnectionFragment  
    OverlayView
    A simple View providing a render callback to other classes.
    RecognitionScoreView  
    RecognizeCommands
    Reads in results from an instantaneous audio recognition model and smoothes them over time.
    RecognizeCommands.RecognitionResult
    Holds information about what's been recognized.
    SpeechActivity
    An activity that listens for audio and then uses a TensorFlow model to detect particular classes, by default a small set of action words.
    StylizeActivity
    Sample activity that stylizes the camera preview according to "A Learned Representation For Artistic Style" (https://arxiv.org/abs/1610.07629)
    TensorFlowImageClassifier
    A classifier specialized to label images using TensorFlow.
    TensorFlowMultiBoxDetector
    A detector for general purpose object detection as described in Scalable Object Detection using Deep Neural Networks (https://arxiv.org/abs/1312.2249).
    TensorFlowObjectDetectionAPIModel
    Wrapper for frozen detection models trained using the Tensorflow Object Detection API: github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/research/object_detection
    TensorFlowYoloDetector
    An object detector that uses TF and a YOLO model to detect objects.
